Deprecated Classes
org.apache.commons.collections15.bag.TypedBag
          Type safety classes not required anymore under 1.5, just use a typed Bag. 
org.apache.commons.collections15.collection.TypedCollection
          Type safe classes are no longer required under 1.5. 
org.apache.commons.collections15.list.TypedList
          Java Generics makes this class obsolete. 
org.apache.commons.collections15.map.TypedMap
          no longer needed with Java generics. 
org.apache.commons.collections15.map.TypedSortedMap
          no longer needed with Java generics.

org.apache.commons.collections15.bidimap.AbstractDualBidiMap.createMap()

          use CollectionUtils.get(Object, int) instead. Will be removed in v4.0 
org.apache.commons.collections15.BagUtils.transformedBag(Bag, Transformer)

org.apache.commons.collections15.BagUtils.transformedSortedBag(SortedBag, Transformer)
